  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2280490/extras/3781741a5fa03c0b01b7dbff155f6528.poster.avif?t=1727886943\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2280490/extras/3781741a5fa03c0b01b7dbff155f6528.webm?t=1727886943\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2280490/extras/3781741a5fa03c0b01b7dbff155f6528.mp4?t=1727886943\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Metal Ascension is a reverse bullet hell, survival game with rogue-lite elements! Defeat the wave of enemies on each floor to level up, install and upgrade your mech and establish fire superiority. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2280490/extras/d7ce9a24bc6e6ab2249cd131c728346e.poster.avif?t=1727886943\" width=402 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2280490/extras/d7ce9a24bc6e6ab2249cd131c728346e.webm?t=1727886943\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2280490/extras/d7ce9a24bc6e6ab2249cd131c728346e.mp4?t=1727886943\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>In this fast-paced, top-down-shooter, use different combinations of weapons and pieces to destroy your enemies. Unlock up to 150 unique pieces to improve your mech. Can you reach the top floor and ascend as a legend?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2280490/extras/d4c3ca443abba5cd9e3ed9e01f2fdb28.poster.avif?t=1727886943\" width=300 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2280490/extras/d4c3ca443abba5cd9e3ed9e01f2fdb28.webm?t=1727886943\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2280490/extras/d4c3ca443abba5cd9e3ed9e01f2fdb28.mp4?t=1727886943\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Features</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Chose between: auto-firing weapons or manual aiming option<br></li><li>Fast runs (under 30 minutes)<br></li><li>Unlock over 150+ pieces to customize and improve your mech<br></li><li>Survive waves lasting 20 to 60 seconds each and kill off as many enemy mechs as you can during that time<br></li><li>Collect materials and get items from the shop between waves of enemies<br></li><li>Gain experience destroying mechs to upgrade your stats</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2280490/extras/3781741a5fa03c0b01b7dbff155f6528.poster.avif?t=1727886943\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2280490/extras/3781741a5fa03c0b01b7dbff155f6528.webm?t=1727886943\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2280490/extras/3781741a5fa03c0b01b7dbff155f6528.mp4?t=1727886943\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Metal Ascension is a reverse bullet hell, survival game with rogue-lite elements! Defeat the wave of enemies on each floor to level up, install and upgrade your mech and establish fire superiority. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2280490/extras/d7ce9a24bc6e6ab2249cd131c728346e.poster.avif?t=1727886943\" width=402 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2280490/extras/d7ce9a24bc6e6ab2249cd131c728346e.webm?t=1727886943\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2280490/extras/d7ce9a24bc6e6ab2249cd131c728346e.mp4?t=1727886943\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>In this fast-paced, top-down-shooter, use different combinations of weapons and pieces to destroy your enemies. Unlock up to 150 unique pieces to improve your mech. Can you reach the top floor and ascend as a legend?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2280490/extras/d4c3ca443abba5cd9e3ed9e01f2fdb28.poster.avif?t=1727886943\" width=300 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2280490/extras/d4c3ca443abba5cd9e3ed9e01f2fdb28.webm?t=1727886943\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2280490/extras/d4c3ca443abba5cd9e3ed9e01f2fdb28.mp4?t=1727886943\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Features</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Chose between: auto-firing weapons or manual aiming option<br></li><li>Fast runs (under 30 minutes)<br></li><li>Unlock over 150+ pieces to customize and improve your mech<br></li><li>Survive waves lasting 20 to 60 seconds each and kill off as many enemy mechs as you can during that time<br></li><li>Collect materials and get items from the shop between waves of enemies<br></li><li>Gain experience destroying mechs to upgrade your stats</li></ul>",
